  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell

    ConwaysGameOfLife
    The Graphical User Interface and entry point to the application.
    InfoPanel
    A Custom JPanel to continuously update labels that display simulation information.
    Persister
    Provides persistence functionality for the application; can load and save worlds.
    Stack
    The stack onto which the simulation pushes and pops world iterations.
    StackNode
    A node in the stack.
    Surface
    A custom JPanel where the world is drawn.
    World
    The world that holds the cells of the simulation.
